      <title>拜登要求2025年国防预算在上限范围内增加1%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/biden-to-request-1-increase-in-2025-defense-budget-under-cap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情官员表示，拜登政府将要求 2025 财年国防开支增加 1%，达到 8498 亿美元，在应对去年债务上限协议规定的上限之际，缩减了更大幅度增长的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/biden-to-request-1-increase-in-2025-defense-budget-under-cap</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 22:48:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
